{"tid":181820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯辯護大狀Peter Pannu曾涉收賄被警隊斷續停職7年後撤職","createTime":"2017-04-01T01:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T04:25:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84dc610a2e23413501d6175b3b99b4f3708d149e","tid":181820,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170401/19976917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170401%2F19976917&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e1cf4773\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170401%2F19976917&h=8f17079d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170401/19976917</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170401/large/a0206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170401%2Flarge%2Fa0206a.gif&h=b6780d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170401/large/a0206b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170401%2Flarge%2Fa0206b.gif&h=38f70abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】辯方大律師彭彼得（Peter Pannu）庭上質疑控方延誤檢控，又投訴朱經緯手臂延伸說法被廣傳，揚言或藉此申終止聆訊，如此落力維護客戶利益的Pannu原來曾任警隊反黑組高級督察，是「印巴雙煞」之一，但多年前因涉收賄及傷人而停職7年，其間獲支薪達400萬元並修讀法律課程成執業大狀，引起社會譁然。<br />\n <br />\n曾任伯明翰CEO　與楊家誠稔熟<br />\n<br />\n現年54歲的Pannu於1985年加入警隊，其後晉升為高級督察，與警隊另一同袍高大偉被冠以「印巴雙煞」。他被指於1993年收受「灣仔之虎」陳耀興賄款，先後接受警隊紀律聆訊及被廉署控以貪污罪而停職，1996年獲無罪釋放，Pannu獲准復職未幾又涉傷人被控，最後同獲無罪釋放。<br />\n<br />\n他斷斷續續被警隊停職近七年，其間「善用時間」完成法律課程，1997年獲認可大律師資格。Pannu於2000年離開警隊私人執業，後來曾任伯明翰環球行政總裁，與因洗黑錢入獄的楊家誠是好友，但2014年底被撤職。<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯昨與Pannu乘坐私家車抵達西九龍法院，身穿一身黑色西裝及佩戴警隊領帶的朱，獲約10名大漢在門外恭候，他們護送朱乘坐升降機，朱踏入升降機後向他們連番表示「唔該晒」。另約30名撐警大聯盟成員早於8時許到庭聲援，大嗌「朱經緯抗暴冇罪，律政司失職要下台！」他們指警察執法含冤，執法反被執法，又謂朱是「榮休人才，光榮無限」。"},{"pid":"7fdf706ec0f289e22b153109e0077d1c159104b0","tid":181820,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"黑警搵返黑大狀辯護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009b58fb3171e6e140d6d92385ed85536d325d0a","tid":181820,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"原來一早警黑一家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31f3f20bdd218354e25af47a283e8268b4873e3","tid":181820,"uid":80944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad87e2149babf4b30237b9f87e8a6c68c0bb7edb","tid":181820,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"黑警一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310e427dd98c08c8e60555882713f7a96ca74c51","tid":181820,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"元祖黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c100416cc1ad96cfd5401d5c3363f702e75add5","tid":181820,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"涉收賄款畀人踢走後可以越撈越掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"44702eb46b6eb258339701a09fdbe916c3b01f81","tid":181820,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"嘩好黑呀"},{"pid":"fa691048f505b4dc0d3a9a4b4530c2e952b15493","tid":181820,"uid":13503,"l